filebeat: filebeat (short desc)
filebeat: Filebeat is a lightweight shipper for forwarding and centralizing
filebeat: log data. Installed as an agent on your servers, Filebeat monitors 
filebeat: the log files or locations  you specify, collects log events, 
filebeat: andforwards them either to Elasticsearch or Logstash for indexing
filebeat:
filebeat: Here's how Filebeat works: When you start Filebeat,
filebeat: it starts one or more inputs that look in the locations you've
filebeat: specified for log data. For each log that Filebeat locates,
filebeat: starts a harvester
